Absolutely nothing of interest at all
in the west wing.

707
00:44:01,305 --> 00:44:03,306
Dusty, dull, very boring.

708
00:44:04,475 --> 00:44:06,768
So, that's the west wing!

709
00:44:06,852 --> 00:44:08,227
Nice going.

