No, wait, please! Please, wait!

733
00:48:19,104 --> 00:48:20,146
No!

734
00:49:30,342 --> 00:49:32,426
Here, now. Don't do that.

735
00:49:36,640 --> 00:49:38,307
Just hold still.

736
